            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1667323242906-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet potato fries </strong>topped with the <strong>chickpea masala</strong> and <strong>kachumber salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining cultured coconut</strong> over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
